"$ guix locate ls\n"
"coreutils@@9.1       /gnu/store/@dots{}-coreutils-9.1/bin/ls\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:4226
msgid "Of course the command works for any file, not just commands:"
